---
title: Creamy Tarragon Chicken with Roasted Red Potatoes and Brussels Sprouts
description: This chicken dish is simple, saucy and crispy! Chicken, potatoes and Brussels sprouts are cooked to perfection and topped with a creamy sauce starring Tarragon and Dijon mustard. They're the perfect partners-in-sauce!
